{
  "stem": "6966.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there we stood.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we walked a little way up the platform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "All together, there were 750 of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then a SS sergeant separated the women to the right, and the men stood where we stood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were-- stood waiting a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, one of the women started to cry and shout.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she walked away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She wanted to be with her husband, amongst us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And halfway, this SS had a club in his hand.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he let the club come down on her head.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The poor woman fell to the ground.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he kicked her in the tummy, a thing I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Immediately, he turned around to the men, put the club on our shoulders, and counted 50 men.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There must be several hundred. 50 men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we had to march away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Everything went so quick then that we had no thought about this woman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "A picture I'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then we marched 20, 30 hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And you had to stop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The road is still there, because I've been seven times to that same place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Now I look to the right, and I see a truck come along.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And a truck stops in front of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I can see a lot of women and children loaded, and in the middle stood my wife and child.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now I notice my wife and child, because I see the face.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I call her name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She couldn't have heard me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She didn't make no movement she had heard me, because the engine of the car was making a noise.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But my wife had made clothes, now, from thick velvet curtains, red velvet curtains, the fashion in Holland at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
